headline: Key GOP Health Care Cuts Ruled Out Of Bounds; UNH, HCA Jump — Briefly
summary: The Senate parliamentarian just threw out key Medicaid and Affordable Care Act spending cuts in the GOP's "Big Beautiful Bill," raising the hurdle to a quick passage.  UnitedHealth Group, Centene and HCA Healthcare led an early rally among S&P 500 managed-care companies and hospital operators.

headline: HCA Healthcare Announces HCA Healthcare Foundation’s $1 Million Grant to Enhance Work With Educate Texas
summary: NASHVILLE, Tenn., June 26, 2025--HCA Healthcare, Inc. (NYSE:HCA), one of the nation’s leading healthcare providers, today announced that the HCA Healthcare Foundation, through its Healthier Tomorrow Fund, will enhance its work with Educate Texas, an initiative of Communities Foundation of Texas, through a new $1 million grant.
